The,electric,imp,is,a,tiny,hardware,module,that,can,be,installed,in,an,electronic,device,Once,installed,it,connects,the,device,with,the,imp,cloud,allowing,it,to,interact,with,software,third,party,services,and,external,servers,The,imp,can,help,users,monitor,the,health,and,activity,of,their,electronic,devices,anytime,anywhere,The,electric,imp,API,enables,developers,to,access,local,hardware,and,remote,cloud,functionality,for,an,imp,device